[ StoryStage - Privacy Policy ]

At StoryStage, we respect your privacy. This app does not collect, store, or share any personal data.

No account registration is required.
No personal information is collected or processed.
No tracking or analytics are used.
We use Game Center data to display your player name and profile image within the app.
Your data stays completely private because we don't collect any.

For any questions, feel free to contact me at luanagerber.dev@gmail.com.